%BB%91c/Thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-ca-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u/poem-cG1xk5Z4_dk8cIpXZBlXEA">Thuỷ điệu ca đầu - 水調歌頭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-ho%C3%A0ng-t%C3%A2y-tu%E1%BA%A7n-nam-kinh-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-01/poem-Q3V2kCl5zAJkXj4_DabgGg">Thượng hoàng tây tuần nam kinh ca kỳ 01 - 上皇西巡南京歌其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-%C4%90%C4%83ng/T%E1%BB%91ng-Nh%E1%BA%A1c-Qu%C3%BD-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ho%C3%A0n-kinh/poem-3aDWftFHvcbz_LQZncZLRA">Tống Nhạc Quý Phương hoàn kinh - 送岳季方還京</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-%C4%90%C4%83ng/author-f0pHwz1tzFQ4ho5N8P_VfQ">Quách Đăng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Xuy-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-ajF-qs_S6kiw3yoVeDT14w">Xuy địch - 吹笛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
